\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Peter burst through his bedroom door.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 We're not running late, are we?!\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0   He knew they were running late.  Paul placed his dishes into the dishwasher as Peter scoured the counter frantically for his keys.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 I am not going to fuck this up for you.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 There\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s nothing to fuck up.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Well I don't want them to wait for you.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 They're not going to, no one even knows if I'm going.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Rebekkah-\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  Peter began to say, then stopped himself.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 No pressure, I'm just saying, let\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s show this girl you can show up places on time.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab As Peter started his car, hardcore began to crackle angrily out of the cold speakers.  Paul entered the car head last, motioning for Peter to turn it down before he was all the way inside.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 How do you listen to that shitty metal all the time?  Isn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t it giving you brain damage?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Hell no.  This is the only kind of music I like.  Just so - raw, do you not feel it?  Great lifting music.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
