\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 What? Just cause I like metal and got some meat on my bones?  You can say what you want, the ladies dig guys that are in shape like this.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
