\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Would you RELAX?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0   Peter turned the volume knob down until it clicked off.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 The only advice you\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 re taking from me so far, is seeing this girl again.  That\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s it.  Anyone would tell you that much.  The rest, just figure it out as you go.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Paul could not decide if this was better or worse advice.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 You know, its really - just, its good to see you.  Like, up and dressed, going out.  This has been a good week for that.  I really just -\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
