\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 One seed is - one plant, right?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Y-yeah, I think that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s generally how it works.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
