\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Paul!  Wow!  I wasn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t expecting to see you here!\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  she jangled up beside him, a packet of seeds and a pair of gloves in her hands.}
