\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Ohh, no, I didn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t - \hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Oh no I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 m kidding that would be . . . \hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Paul already felt ridiculous.  Every set of words that tumbled out of his mouth stung his lips painfully.  }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Well luckily I have plenty of those.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0   Rebekkah pulled a packet of carrot seeds from her back pocket.  They were warm with body heat in Paul's hand; the tiny envelope had sealed itself shut from the hummitidy of the day.  }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Radishes!  Back wall - keep \hich\f0 \lquote \loch\f0 em straight.  You see where we dug the rows?  Just start over by Jacob over there.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  she pointed to the neat looking boy that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 d been contimplating seeds a moment before.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Oh shoot, I should have introduced you while you were both here.  You probably don't recognize anyone, huh?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Ah, no.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0   Was that really a point of concern?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Yeah, these guys are from Calvary.  Homeschooled kids.  They do this thing,\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  she explained, \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Where they make them all get together and interact with each other?  Like, they have group P.E. classes where they all play dodgeball.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Paul examined the kids in the garden, and it made sense - they seemed to vary in age slightly, and all had this sort of frightened look to them.  He imagined what sort of pathetic game of dodgeball was played between these people.  They averted their eyes when he looked at them.  It was a huge relief.}
