\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Well that went well.  Paul dug his spade into the hot, dry dirt that bit at his bare knees.  A girl a few rows down had giant kneepads.  Why hadn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t Peter thought of that?  He could already feel a sunburn starting on his neck.  If it was possible to garden bitterly, Paul was pulling it off quite well.  Rebekkah stood at the other side of the garden by the rusted table.  Paul felt silly for coming.  He had no actual desire to plant radishes.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 You have to move faster if you want them all to sprout at the same time!\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0   }
