\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 You have to get them in there all about the same time, to make sure they all pop up at the same time; otherwise the watering\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll get off.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 I don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t think that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s how it works.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  Paul replied, turning his shoulder against Jacob and attempting to plant faster.  Jacob picked up the pace as well, passing him until they both aimed their spade at the same patch of dirt.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Whattaya say?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  Jacob propositioned.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 We both throw our seeds in, and see what they turn into?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
