\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll be honest, this is my first time gardening.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  Jacob explained.  }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Rebekkah walked around handing out sandwiches, using the period of exhange to check in with the gardeners about their day.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Things going well?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  Paul could hear her ask.  \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Need anything?\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 , and things also like \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Yeah, I didn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t have anything better to do this weekend\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  and \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 That\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s interesting, tell me about it.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0 }
